./sdp/logs/Lead_T-007_20260408T223256Z_1775691000.log:8220:The Dell PowerEdge R750 (2x Xeon Silver 4310, 813GB RAM, no GPU) will run PromptClaw with Ollama as a first-class local agent alongside claude/codex/gemini. This PRD covers the code changes needed to integrate Ollama into the existing daemon architecture. No architectural rewrites — extend what exists.
